{{!-- Header --}}
<h2 class="tripheader text-center" id="tripreview-header" style="color:#c49e6b;">Trip Review Form</h2>

<div class="container-fluid">
   <form class="myForm center" id="myForm">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 nameinput" id="review-form-fn">
            <label for="validationServer01">First name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control is-valid" id="firstName" placeholder="First name" required>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 nameinput" id="review-form-ln">
            <label for="validationServer02">Last name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control is-valid" id="lastName" placeholder="Last name" required>
          </div>
        </div>

          <p>1. How would you rate the quality of the trip?</p>
          <select class="custom-select col-sm-12 col-md-offset-1 forminput" id="Q1">
            <option selected disabled>1 - Unsatisfactory, 5 - The BEST</option>
            <option value="1">One</option>
            <option value="2">Two</option>
            <option value="3">Three</option>
            <option value="4">Four</option>
            <option value="5">Five</option>
          </select>

          <p>2. How would you rate the quality of information provided to you?</p>
          <select class="custom-select col-sm-12 col-md-offset-1 forminput" id="Q2">
            <option selected disabled>1 - Unsatisfactory, 5 - The BEST</option>
            <option value="1">One</option>
            <option value="2">Two</option>
            <option value="3">Three</option>
            <option value="4">Four</option>
            <option value="5">Five</option>
          </select>

          <p>3. How likely are you to recommend this trip to your friends and family?</p>
          <select class="custom-select col-sm-12 col-md-offset-1 forminput" id="Q3">
            <option selected disabled>1 - Probably Not, 5 - Absolutely!</option>
            <option value="1">One</option>
            <option value="2">Two</option>
            <option value="3">Three</option>
            <option value="4">Four</option>
            <option value="5">Five</option>
          </select>

          <p>4. How likely are you to do this again?</p>
          <select class="custom-select col-sm-12 col-md-offset-1 forminput" id="Q4">
            <option selected disabled>1 - Probably Not, 5 - Absolutely!</option>
            <option value="1">One</option>
            <option value="2">Two</option>
            <option value="3">Three</option>
            <option value="4">Four</option>
            <option value="5">Five</option>
          </select>

          <p>5. How would you rate the usability of our web interface?</p>
          <select class="custom-select col-sm-12 col-md-offset-1 forminput" id="Q5">
            <option selected disabled>1 - Hate it, 5 - Amazing!</option>
            <option value="1">One</option>
            <option value="2">Two</option>
            <option value="3">Three</option>
            <option value="4">Four</option>
            <option value="5">Five</option>
          </select>

          <div class="form-group col-sm-12 col-md-offset-1 forminput" id="review-text">
            <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1">Review Comments</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="comments" rows="5"></textarea>
          </div>

        <div class="col-md-10 mb-3">
          <button type="submit" class="btn" id="submitReview" style="background-color: #1f2c38; color: #96a515">Submit Review</button>
        </div>
      </form>
</div>

